
airs2cris -- an overview of the AIRS to CrIS translation

decon -- a more detailed writeup of the IASI to CrIS, IASI to AIRS,
AIRS to CrIS, and CrIS to AIRS translations.  DRAFT VERSION.

finterp.pdf -- some useful notes on interferometric interpolation.
The latex source is from ccast/doc

decon_old -- early version of a more detailed AIRS deconvolution
writup, the useful parts should subsumed by decon as it develops.

notes_old -- assorted old notes, the useful parts should subsumed 
by decon as it develops


The asl blog posts give a good overview of how these ideas were
developed.  These are listed in chronological order, with the second
group probably the most useful.

  http://hyperearth.wordpress.com/2013/07/24/airs-to-cris-translations/
  http://hyperearth.wordpress.com/2013/11/04/airs-to-cris-translation-update/
  http://hyperearth.wordpress.com/2013/11/12/airs-to-cris-updates/
  http://hyperearth.wordpress.com/2014/07/22/first-look-at-an-iasi-to-airs-translation/
  http://hyperearth.wordpress.com/2014/07/22/interferometric-interpolation/

  https://hyperearth.wordpress.com/2014/10/31/airs-to-cris-validation-summary/
  https://hyperearth.wordpress.com/2014/10/31/iasi-to-cris-translations/
  https://hyperearth.wordpress.com/2014/10/27/iasi-to-airs-refinements/

